                           Fase 2: Parte Privada
                    






                            FIREWALL 1:
                                        VPN > IPSEC

                                        Description: <NOME DO VIZINHO>
                                        Internet Protocol: IPV4
                                        INTERFACE: WAN
                                        REMOTE GATEWAY: <IP PUBLICO DO VIZINHO>
